'''天主教伊莫拉教區'''（{{lang-la|Diocesis Imolensis}}）是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在[[意大利|意大利]]北部[[艾米利亚-罗马涅|艾米利亚-罗马涅]]大区[[博洛尼亚|博洛尼亚]]省设立的一个教区。现在是[[天主教博洛尼亚总教区|天主教博洛尼亚总教区]]的附属教区。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dimol.html |title=''Catholic Hierarchy'' page |access-date=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027024341/https://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dimol.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

現任教區主教為{{link-it|若望·莫夏蒂|Giovanni Mosciatti}}，榮休主教為{{link-it|多默·吉雷利|Tommaso Ghirelli}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 31.05.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/31/190531c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817060310/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/31/190531c.html |archivedate=2019-08-17 |language=en |date=2019-05-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

